name: How are you? (Ps. A Random Thoughts Collection)
description:
This visual represent the expression of people who are already 
tired but keep on going in the path that they have choose to take. Already exhausted in this world full of distraction and negative vibration but still giving their best to succeed, staying as a good people and keep on doing art  to express their creativity. 

"We are all tired and exhausted, but here I am. I feel (just like) you."
